title: "canvodpy: GNSS Vegetation Optical Depth Analysis"
abstract: >
  canvodpy is a Python package for calculating Vegetation Optical Depth (VOD)
  from GNSS (Global Navigation Satellite System) signal-to-noise ratio (SNR) data.
  It provides tools for GNSS data reading, auxiliary data handling, grid operations,
  storage, visualization, and VOD calculation algorithms.
